rows.label: qst105608_msg001
rows.name:
There are rebel soldiers trying
to gain Adel's recognition.

rows.label: qst105608_msg0001
rows.name: Ooh... Our valiant hero, Adel-sama!!

rows.label: qst105608_msg0002
rows.name:
We offer this book in which
a false oath is written...

rows.label: qst105608_msg0003
rows.name: Adel-sama! Appear before us...!

rows.label: qst105608_msg0004
rows.name:
Punish the false king who has
thrown the people into chaos!

rows.label: qst105608_msg0005
rows.name: That's enough!

rows.label: qst105608_msg0006
rows.name:
...Zeke! Why is the
prodigal prince here?!

rows.label: qst105608_msg0007
rows.name:
This weird ritual game is over!
There's no way Adel is comin'.

rows.label: qst105608_msg0008
rows.name:
This is not a game! It is
a sacred ritual for the
revival of Adel-sama!

rows.label: qst105608_msg0009
rows.name:
So where's Adel? He's not here yet?
Is he runnin' late or somethin'?

rows.label: qst105608_msg0010
rows.name: Grr... How dare you mock us!!

rows.label: qst105608_msg0011
rows.name:
Just you watch... Adel-sama
will soon be revived!

rows.label: qst105608_msg0012
rows.name:
And he will eradicate the royal
family that has deceived the
people of Luxuria for 500 years!

rows.label: qst105608_msg0013
rows.name:
Ah, no good, no good.
Prince, this is no good.

rows.label: qst105608_msg0014
rows.name:
They don't seem like they're in a
state for a proper conversation.

rows.label: qst105608_msg0015
rows.name: ...Yeah.

rows.label: qst105608_msg0016
rows.name:
I know we've done you all a great
wrong... ...mostly my old man.

rows.label: qst105608_msg0017
rows.name:
But eradicating us won't solve
any of the country's problems!

rows.label: qst105608_msg0018
rows.name:
As long as we live, we'll pay
back the debt for our lies!

rows.label: qst105608_msg0019
rows.name: Enough talk! I'm stoppin' you!!
